8
00:01:05,231 --> 00:01:07,600
-Don't you agree?
-Why are you asking me?

9
00:01:07,667 --> 00:01:09,803
-Don't you agree?
-Why are you asking me?

10
00:01:10,003 --> 00:01:14,541
I'm going to watch her.
And if she does it wrong, I'll report her.

11
00:01:14,741 --> 00:01:15,809
Just you see.

12
00:01:17,977 --> 00:01:18,978
Good luck!

13
00:01:27,987 --> 00:01:31,424
It's your turn, counsel.

14
00:01:35,028 --> 00:01:38,798
