How can she say that?

36
00:03:33,279 --> 00:03:38,384
You witnessed the defendant
pushing Mun Dong-hui, right?

37
00:03:38,818 --> 00:03:39,786
Yes.

38
00:03:40,887 --> 00:03:44,057
I heard Dong-hui and Seong-bin fighting.

39
00:03:44,724 --> 00:03:46,326
Then I heard a thud.

40
00:03:46,659 --> 00:03:49,462
And Dong-hui was lying on the flower bed.

41
00:03:52,165 --> 00:03:53,199
That's all.

42
00:03:55,068 --> 00:03:58,438
You said you looked
after you heard the thud.

43
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:04,110
So you didn't actually see
the defendant push the victim.

44
00:04:04,377 --> 00:04:05,378
What?

45
00:04:09,382 --> 00:04:11,584
No, but...

46
00:04:11,985 --> 00:04:14,020
You said you looked
after you heard a thud.

47
00:04:15,555 --> 00:04:17,023
Let me ask again.

48
00:04:17,523 --> 00:04:23,229
Did you witness Ko Seong-bin
push Mun Dong-hui yourself?

49
00:04:24,063 --> 00:04:26,499
No, but it's the same thing.

50
00:04:27,166 --> 00:04:30,103
