151
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:04,250
Hey, Mun Dong-hui!
You can't do this to me!

152
00:13:04,316 --> 00:13:06,051
Sit down and put the wig back on.

153
00:13:06,118 --> 00:13:07,787
You sit down!

154
00:13:07,853 --> 00:13:11,724
