206
00:16:57,783 --> 00:17:01,086
-Do you know who I lost to?
-Do I have to know that?

207
00:17:01,153 --> 00:17:03,989
-It's Do-yeon. Seo Do-yeon.
-So what?

208
00:17:04,223 --> 00:17:07,426
