248
00:19:47,085 --> 00:19:50,122
Jun-guk. Min Jun-guk.

249
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:03,936
If you almost died,
you should live properly!

250
00:20:04,002 --> 00:20:06,505
My goddamn life is going to be ruined
because of that brat!

251
00:20:06,738 --> 00:20:09,441
Let me go!
I'll die if I don't do something!

252
00:20:11,443 --> 00:20:13,812
